public class NotificationResponse
extends SynchronousResponse

This class encapsulates the result of a NotificationRequest. For each target to be notified in the original NotificationRequest, a NotificationResponse contains one instance of SingleTargetNotificationResponse.

Method Detail

getResponses

public SingleTargetNotificationResponse[] getResponses()
Gets the SingleTargetNotificationResponses off all the notified targets.

Returns:
The SingleTargetNotificationResponses of all the notified targets in the same order as the target user ids specified in the original NotificationRequest. Note that these are only returned if and only if the original NotificationRequest was to be aknowledged, compare NotificationRequest.DO_ACK and NotificationRequest.NO_ACK. Otherwise, null is returned.
